data3 <- dataclean

for (i in 1:nrow(data3)){ 
  if (is.na(data3[i,"steps"])){
    int <- data3[i,"interval"]
    data3[i,"steps"] <- steps2[steps2$Group.1 == int,][[2]] 
    }
  }


steps3 <- aggregate(data3[,"steps"], by = list(data3$date), FUN = sum)
